text: Gerard van Vliet (born 26 February 1964) is an Aruban former cyclist. He competed in the individual road race at the 1992 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1964 births Category:Living people Category:Aruban male cyclists Category:Olympic cyclists of Aruba Category:Cyclists at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
